Entourage is a 2015 American comedy film written , directed and co-produced by Doug Ellin .
It serves as a continuation of the HBO TV series of the same name created by Ellin .
It stars the principal cast of the show , Kevin Connolly , Adrian Grenier , Kevin Dillon , Jerry Ferrara and Jeremy Piven .
The film was released on June 3 , 2015 , received generally negative reviews and grossed over $ 49 million .